snippet.title: v7.4 Invitation to the Mad Banquet Trailer — Honkai Impact 3rd
snippet.description:
Honkai Impact 3rd v7.4 Invitation to the Mad Banquet coming soon! New S-rank battlesuit Mad Pleasure: Shadowbringer joins the fight.
Part 2 Main Story Chapter II The Seven Shus in the Maze and featured event Flying to Oxia Invitation Contest will also be available. Stay tuned!

Voice Artists:
Thelema: Akira Sekine
"Lantern": Yumiri Hanamori
Dreamseeker: Yuki Nakashima
